    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>Tutanota is the world's most secure email service, easy to use and private by design. Sign up for free encrypted email now.

With end-to-end encryption and 2FA, your emails have never been more secure. The built-in encryption guarantees that your mailbox belongs to you: Nobody can decrypt or read your data.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>Tutanota is an email client with a strong focus on security and privacy that lets you encrypt emails on all your devices.</summary>
    <releaseNotes># What's new
 - Timezones for events [#10493](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10493)
 - Update search results list after partially indexed and fully indexed [#11196](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11196)
 - Update `reIndexLocalData_msg` for full-archive-download indexing [#11131](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11131)
 - Add logging to failed-to-export mail [#11125](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11125)
 - Show reminders in event preview [#11124](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11124)
 - Re-add "Failed-to-delete folders" section [#11081](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11081)
 - Offline migration for new indexer [#11015](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11015)
 - Implement Resume Indexing [#10969](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10969)
 - Change how websocket close event is logged to better see information [#10967](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10967)
 - Implement cancelMailIndexing for OfflineStorageIndexer [#10920](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10920)
 - Allow clearing cache without clearing credentials [#10919](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10919)
 - Remove Local data's offline range section from setting [#10917](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10917)
 - Improve drag and drop indication [#10914](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10914)

# Bugfixes
 - BadRequestError when searching for contacts using OfflineDB [#11050](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11050)
 - repeatRules.excludedDates does not contain synthetic entries from altered instances when syncing external calendar [#11034](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11034)
 - timeZone not set on repeat rule causes many request on first sync [#11025](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11025)
 - Event invitation shows as ghost bubble even for the organiser when its part of a shared calendar [#11011](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/11011)
 - [web] Web Socket closed by SleepDetector when indexing a lot of large mails received on the same day [#10973](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10973)
 - Importing events with alarms setup for notifications and email can result and duplicated alarms [#10972](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10972)
 - Clicking open on attachment bubble in the mail editor downloads attachment [#10915](https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/issues/10915)

# Milestone
https://github.com/tutao/tutanota/milestone/446?closed=1


